Zm_lila_panic_sicfix_v2



Lila_panic_v1 is the most popular map on zombie mod, but so boring

so I made the best map ever zm_lila_panic_sicfix_v2.



the map is bigger than lila_panic, so there are more cade places, hidding spots and places to have a nice death.

there are 7 secrets in the map, I'm willing to show them to you if you want to (contact me on sic.gamer@hotmail.com)




version 1 has been tested for 2 months on two differend servers and has been having good comments of noobs as well as pro gamers
in version 2 this version all the bugs of v1 have been fixed, and the map has been increased in size as well



you guys are free to change the map or coppy parts of it. (but remember me and put my name in your map)




maybe there will come a v3 so report anny bugs or good ideas to me






enjoy gaming on my map


greetings Sic.
